===Noun===
'''畜生''' ([[ちくしょう]], ''[[chikushō]]'')

# ''(Buddhism)'' A generic term for [[animal]]s, [[bird]]s, [[fish]] and [[insect]]s, as the [[reincarnate]]d form of one who had bad [[karma]] in a previous life.
# An [[immoral]] person; an "[[animal]]".

===Interjection===
'''畜生''' ([[ちくしょう]], ''[[chikushō]]'')

# [[Damn]], [[dammit]].

